          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The four  measurements  of the excitation function of",
                " the   reaction   Li-7(g,p)He-6   reported   in   the",
                " literature show major disagreements.  In the present",
                " experiment the excitation function was measured from",
                " 10  to 32 MeV and the integrated cross section up to",
                " 34 MeV was determined as 14.6(3.4) MeV*mb.  No major",
                " structure   was   observed   in  the  shape  of  the",
                " activation curve which indicates a  broad  resonance",
                " with  appreciable  cross  sections up to the maximum",
                " energy investigated."
              ]
            }
          ],
